    <item>
      <title>以色列称与哈马斯在加沙停火问题上仍存在巨大分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/israel-says-large-gaps-remain-with-hamas-over-gaza-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列官员表示，以色列和哈马斯之间的停火谈判再次陷入僵局，双方在人质、囚犯和加沙的未来问题上存在巨大分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/israel-says-large-gaps-remain-with-hamas-over-gaza-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 08:30:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究称爱尔兰需要大幅增税来资助统一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ireland-would-need-big-tax-rise-to-fund-unification-study-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的研究表明，爱尔兰的统一需要大幅增税并削减公共支出，该研究揭示了爱尔兰共和国未来与北爱尔兰统一的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/ireland-would-need-big-tax-rise-to-fund-unification-study-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 08:29:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
